title: Haretara Kimi o Mukae ni Iku
description:
A collection of stories:

1) Haretara Kimi wo Mukaeniiku 

2-6) Ore wa Kawaii Otouto to (My Cute Little Brother and I Are...)
A kinky relationship of two brothers

7) Pero Pero Chan (Licking Chan)
A pet store mascot dog falls in love with one of the unsold puppies in his owner's shop. Also in Erohon Bukkake
